## Debian bookworm mirror

deb [arch=amd64] http://deb.debian.org/debian bookworm main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
deb-src [arch=amd64] http://deb.debian.org/debian bookworm main contrib non-free non-free-firmware

deb [arch=amd64] http://deb.debian.org/debian bookworm-updates main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
deb-src [arch=amd64] http://deb.debian.org/debian bookworm-updates main contrib non-free non-free-firmware

deb [arch=amd64] http://security.debian.org/debian-security bookworm-security main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
deb-src [arch=amd64] http://security.debian.org/debian-security bookworm-security main contrib non-free non-free-firmware
